The GREATEST pizza ever 🍕 🍕🍕@papavpizza806

I used to be a pizza delivery guy for my paisano when he owned the shop in Las Vegas!

It was truly one of my favorite jobs I have ever had! I really enjoyed the family feel and authentic pizza that was being made just like it was straight from Italy 🇮🇹 

I definitely have great memories of getting my paisano an espresso everyday to keep him energized to make the best pizza and making deliveries to houses on the weekends to people who were the biggest fans of his pizza shop!

I met some amazing people that would come into the pizzeria everyday just because they loved how they were treated and taken care of. 

The pizza that he makes is not just any pizza to him but he takes pride in what he does and makes it from his heart! 

Writing this post just brings GIANT SMILES to my face because of all the great memories that I had there!

Now he has his new location out in Lubbock, Texas and if you haven’t tried his pizza…you are missing out!! 

If you are in the Lubbock area you should check out @papavpizza806 

Thank you for always treating me like family 🇮🇹🙏🏿

Ad hooks are incredibly important when it comes to your advertising! 

You should spend 90-95% of your time on the ad hook since if it’s not engaging enough it will not capture your targeted audiences attention which means they won’t consume the content! 

If they don’t consume the content then everything else that you say in the rest of your content doesn’t matter because they would of never consumed it.

If they don’t consume it then they can’t get a better understanding of how you can help them achieve their goals! 

So focus on your ad hooks! 

#marketing #socialmediamarketing

What an unbelievable retreat Mike Burnett constructed in Park City, Utah! 

What he has put together is simply incredible and I am honored to be in the mastermind group called Prosper360!

At the latest retreat I witnessed one of the most transformative experiences I have EVER seen in person!

Dr. Forbes Riley (@forbes_riley )demonstrated what being a good human being is truly all about! 

She has all of the accolades you can imagine selling over 2 Billion dollars worth of products and being the ultimate pitch woman! 

But it was her heart that touched this group of entrepreneurs so we have Chip Hopper to thank🙏🏿

What I love so much about the group is it is not ONLY about growing your business but in my opinion it is about the MOST important part of life…true connection and family! 

In this group that is facilitated by the man that is KNOWN AS… the coach of the 1 percenters Lane Monson he orchestrates one of the greatest exercises I have seen which is the hot seats! 

The hot seats are designed to allow the members to share a challenge/opportunity to the rest of the group and then get actionable feedback from HIGHLY successful and empathetic entrepreneurs who have achieved BIG things… how cool is that?! 

I am incredibly grateful for the experience I had over the last few days and I HIGHLY recommend if you are looking for a group that can take you to the next level PROSPER 360 would be a perfect fit for you! 🙏🏿
